ttp_template:
<group name="destination_from_name_nat_type">
  nat-type {{NAT_TYPE | ORPHRASE}};
  to {{FROM | ORPHRASE}};
  destination {{SOURCE | ORPHRASE}};
  service  {{SERVICE | ORPHRASE}};
  terminal {{TERMINAL | ORPHRASE}};
{{NAME | ORPHRASE}} {
  destination {{DESTINATION | ORPHRASE}};
  translate-to "{{TRANSLATE_TO | ORPHRASE}}";
</group>
textfsm_template:
Value Filldown NAME (.*?)
Value Required NAT_TYPE (\S+)
Value FROM (\S+|\[(\s\S+)+\s\])
# any  |  ip (optional mask)  |  [ multiIP ]
Value SOURCE (any|([A-Fa-f0-9:\.]+(\/\d+)?)|\[(\s[A-Fa-f0-9:\.]+(\/\d+)?)+\s\])
Value TO (\S+|\[(\s\S+)+\s\])
Value TO_INTERFACE (\S*)
Value DESTINATION (\S+|\[(\s\S+)+\s\])
Value SERVICE ([\S+\s+]+)
Value TRANSLATE_TO ([\S+\s+]+)
Value TERMINAL (\S+)

Start
  ^${NAME}\s+\{$$
  ^\s+nat-type\s+${NAT_TYPE};$$
  ^\s+from\s+${FROM};$$
  ^\s+source\s+${SOURCE};$$ 
  ^\s+to\s+${TO};$$
  ^.+to-interface\s${TO_INTERFACE}\s?;$$
  ^\s+destination\s+${DESTINATION};$$
  ^\s+service\s+${SERVICE};$$
  ^\s+translate-to\s+"${TRANSLATE_TO}";$$
  ^\s+terminal\s+${TERMINAL};$$
  ^}$$ -> Record
  ^. -> Error
